<refsect2 id='sect.config_setup'>
  <title>
    Config Setup Section
  </title>
  <para>
    The <option>config setup</option> section overrides preset
    configuration parameters.  For instance, to change the location of
    &pluto;'s log file, include a <option>config setup</option>
    section containing:
  </para>

  <programlisting><xi:include
  href="d.ipsec.conf/config_setup.example"
  parse="text"
  xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"/></programlisting>

  <para>
    To display a configuration parameter's preset, the command
    <command>ipsec addconn --configsetup
    <replaceable>parameter</replaceable></command> can be used.  This
    is especially useful for obtaining the location of directories,
    such as the &NSS; Database directory, that vary across systems.
  </para>

  <para>
    The currently-accepted configuration parameters are:
    <variablelist>
      &setup.audit-log;
      &setup.crl-strict;
      &setup.crl-timeout;
      &setup.crlcheckinterval;
      &setup.curl-iface;
      &setup.ddos-ike-threshold;
      &setup.ddos-mode;
      &setup.dns-resolver;
      &setup.dnssec-anchors;
      &setup.dnssec-enable;
      &setup.dnssec-rootkey-file;
      &setup.dumpdir;
      &setup.exampledir;
      &setup.expire-lifetime;
      &setup.expire-shunt-interval;
      &setup.global-redirect-to;
      &setup.global-redirect;
      &setup.ike-socket-bufsize;
      &setup.ike-socket-errqueue;
      &setup.ikev1-policy;
      &setup.ipsec-interface-managed;
      &setup.ipsecdir;
      &setup.keep-alive;
      &setup.listen-tcp;
      &setup.listen-udp;
      &setup.listen;
      &setup.logappend;
      &setup.logfile;
      &setup.logip;
      &setup.loglimit;
      &setup.logtime;
      &setup.max-halfopen-ike;
      &setup.myvendorid;
      &setup.nflog-all;
      &setup.nhelpers;
      &setup.nssdir;
      &setup.ocsp-cache-max-age;
      &setup.ocsp-cache-min-age;
      &setup.ocsp-cache-size;
      &setup.ocsp-enable;
      &setup.ocsp-method;
      &setup.ocsp-strict;
      &setup.ocsp-timeout;
      &setup.ocsp-trustname;
      &setup.ocsp-uri;
      &setup.plutodebug;
      &setup.protostack;
      &setup.seccomp;
      &setup.secretsfile;
      &setup.seedbits;
      &setup.shuntlifetime;
      &setup.statsbin;
      &setup.syslog;
      &setup.uniqueids;
      &setup.virtual-private;
    </variablelist>
  </para>
</refsect2>
